    <entry>
      <title>python基础语法</title>
      <link href="/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/"/>
      <url>/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="python基础"><a href="#python基础" class="headerlink" title="python基础"></a>python基础</h1><h1 id="基础数据类型"><a href="#基础数据类型" class="headerlink" title="基础数据类型"></a>基础数据类型</h1><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">数字:1 , 2 , 3 , 4浮点数:1.2 ,1123.777字符串: &quot;1&quot;,&quot;234&quot;boolean: True,False<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h1 id="注释"><a href="#注释" class="headerlink" title="注释"></a>注释</h1><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">#单行注释&quot;&quot;&quot;多行注释&quot;&quot;&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h1 id="输出"><a href="#输出" class="headerlink" title="输出"></a>输出</h1><p>输出内容到显示屏: </p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">print()<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>输出内容到文件中</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">fp &#x3D; open(&#39;test.txt&#39;,&#39;a+&#39;)print(&#39;hello&#39;,file&#x3D;fp)fp.close()<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>不换行输出</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">print(&quot;1&quot;,&quot;1&quot;,&quot;1&quot;)<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h1 id="强制类型转化"><a href="#强制类型转化" class="headerlink" title="强制类型转化"></a>强制类型转化</h1><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">a&#x3D;1其他类型转化为字符串: a&#x3D;str(a)其他类型强制转化为数字 a&#x3D;int(a)其他类型强制转化为浮点型 a&#x3D;float(a)<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h1 id="输入"><a href="#输入" class="headerlink" title="输入"></a>输入</h1><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">a&#x3D;input(&quot;请输入一个数&quot;)input()返回一个str类型如果输入的值为10,此时a的类型为字符串<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h1 id="运算符"><a href="#运算符" class="headerlink" title="运算符"></a>运算符</h1><p>算术运算符</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/image-20220924100118300.png" class="" title="image-20220924100118300"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/image-20220924100228812.png" class="" title="image-20220924100228812"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/image-20220924100252484.png" class="" title="image-20220924100252484"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/image-20220924100332292.png" class="" title="image-20220924100332292"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/image-20220924100356142.png" class="" title="image-20220924100356142"><h1 id="流程控制语句"><a href="#流程控制语句" class="headerlink" title="流程控制语句"></a>流程控制语句</h1><h2 id="选择结构-if"><a href="#选择结构-if" class="headerlink" title="选择结构:if"></a>选择结构:if</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">if a&#x3D;&#x3D;1 :a&#x3D;2elif a&#x3D;&#x3D;2 :a&#x3D;3else:a&#x3D;4<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="循环结构-for-while"><a href="#循环结构-for-while" class="headerlink" title="循环结构:for,while"></a>循环结构:for,while</h2><h2 id="1-for-in结构"><a href="#1-for-in结构" class="headerlink" title="1.for in结构"></a>1.for in结构</h2><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/image-20220924100731119.png" class="" title="image-20220924100731119"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">r &#x3D; range(10)print(r)print(list(r))<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/24/python-ji-chu-yu-fa/image-20220924100906812.png" class="" title="image-20220924100906812"><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">list()函数用于查看range对象中的整数序列<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="2-while结构"><a href="#2-while结构" class="headerlink" title="2.while结构"></a>2.while结构</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">while true:print(1)<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><h2 id="3-break-continue-pass"><a href="#3-break-continue-pass" class="headerlink" title="3.break,continue,pass"></a>3.break,continue,pass</h2><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">break:跳出当前循环循语句continue: 结束当前循环pass: 语句什么也不做,只是一个占位符,用在语法中需要语句的地方<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>]]></content>
      
      
