    <entry>
      <title>怎么在自己的github上发布项目</title>
      <link href="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-zai-zi-ji-de-github-shang-fa-bu-xiang-mu/"/>
      <url>/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-zai-zi-ji-de-github-shang-fa-bu-xiang-mu/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-新建一个仓库"><a href="#1-新建一个仓库" class="headerlink" title="1.新建一个仓库"></a>1.新建一个仓库</h1><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-zai-zi-ji-de-github-shang-fa-bu-xiang-mu/image-20220922122509160.png" class="" title="image-20220922122509160"><p>没什么好说的，取个名，然后把readme 选中就好</p><h1 id="2-在本地新建文件夹放github文件"><a href="#2-在本地新建文件夹放github文件" class="headerlink" title="2.在本地新建文件夹放github文件"></a>2.在本地新建文件夹放github文件</h1><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git clone https:&#x2F;&#x2F;github.com&#x2F;jcxj&#x2F;ip_to_company.git<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>直接clone就好</p><p><strong>或者</strong>新建一个文件夹然后</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git init<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><h1 id="3-正常的开发流程"><a href="#3-正常的开发流程" class="headerlink" title="3.正常的开发流程"></a>3.正常的开发流程</h1><p>在开发前，先</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git pull origin master<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>该写写，该删删</p><h1 id="4-提交到远程仓库"><a href="#4-提交到远程仓库" class="headerlink" title="4.提交到远程仓库"></a>4.提交到远程仓库</h1><p><strong>如果是第一次则需要配置下远程仓库的地址</strong></p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git remote add name address<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>name是你自己随便取一个名字，方便记忆即可</p><p>xxxx为图中画红线的部分</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-zai-zi-ji-de-github-shang-fa-bu-xiang-mu/image-20220922123216188.png" class="" title="image-20220922123216188"><p>以图中仓库为例，命令应该长这样</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git remote add ip_to_company git@github.com:jcxj&#x2F;ip_to_company.git<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>添加好远程仓库后，用以下命令查看下</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git remote -v<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-zai-zi-ji-de-github-shang-fa-bu-xiang-mu/image-20220922123447882.png" class="" title="image-20220922123447882"><p>长这样就ok了</p><p><strong>下面开始介绍推送到远程仓库常用的命令</strong></p><h3 id="1-git-add"><a href="#1-git-add" class="headerlink" title="1.git add"></a>1.git add</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git add .  <span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p>将文件夹下所有文件提交到本地的缓存区中，也就是.git文件夹</p><h3 id="2-git-commit"><a href="#2-git-commit" class="headerlink" title="2.git commit"></a>2.git commit</h3><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git commit -m &quot;test&quot;<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-zai-zi-ji-de-github-shang-fa-bu-xiang-mu/image-20220922123809243.png" class="" title="image-20220922123809243"><p>跟留言有点像，用来解释说明本次改动具体改了什么</p><h3 id="3-git-push"><a href="#3-git-push" class="headerlink" title="3.git push"></a>3.git push</h3><p>把.git缓存中的文件推送到远程仓库</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">git push origin master<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span></span></code></pre><p><strong>其实，在这些步骤之前还得配置下账号密码什么的，因为我早就配置过了，并且现在给忘了怎么搞，因此就不写了，具体的教程可以去google搜索</strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> github </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
