    <entry>
      <title>怎么翻墙</title>
      <link href="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/"/>
      <url>/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-下载好管理软件"><a href="#1-下载好管理软件" class="headerlink" title="1.下载好管理软件"></a>1.下载好管理软件</h1><p>clash或者v2rayN都行</p><p><a href="https://github.com/Dreamacro/clash">https://github.com/Dreamacro/clash</a></p><p><a href="https://github.com/2dust/v2rayN/releases">https://github.com/2dust/v2rayN/releases</a></p><h1 id="2-购买机场节点"><a href="#2-购买机场节点" class="headerlink" title="2.购买机场节点"></a>2.购买机场节点</h1><p><a href="https://0.azureedge.net/auth/register">登录 — 最萌の云.超新星机场.顶级节点服务商 (azureedge.net)</a></p><p><a href="https://www.cyanmori.com/auth/register">登录 — 青森Cloud (cyanmori.com)</a></p><p>机场节点网上非常非常多自己花点钱去买就好了</p><p>我用的是一元机场,网址如下</p><p><a href="https://一元机场.com/#/dashboard">一元机场 (xn–4gq62f52gdss.com)</a></p><h1 id="3-配置翻墙软件"><a href="#3-配置翻墙软件" class="headerlink" title="3.配置翻墙软件"></a>3.配置翻墙软件</h1><p>无非就是更新订阅</p><h2 id="在你购买后，机场会给你一条订阅"><a href="#在你购买后，机场会给你一条订阅" class="headerlink" title="在你购买后，机场会给你一条订阅"></a>在你购买后，机场会给你一条订阅</h2><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922110937526.png" class="" title="image-20220922110937526"><p>点击复制后，进入你的代理软件，这里以v2rayN为例</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922111045338.png" class="" title="image-20220922111045338"><p>点进去</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922111110448.png" class="" title="image-20220922111110448"><p>把你获得的订阅链接填到地址(url)后面的空白处</p><p>添加好后直接看下方的确定即可</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922111240346.png" class="" title="image-20220922111240346"><p>配置后应该长这样，点击确定后，回到主页面，点击更新订阅(不通过代理)</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922111317701.png" class="" title="image-20220922111317701"><p>然后就会刷新一堆东西出来</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922111416008.png" class="" title="image-20220922111416008"><p>到这一步，如果没什么问题的话，就成功了</p><h1 id="4-常用命令"><a href="#4-常用命令" class="headerlink" title="4.常用命令"></a>4.常用命令</h1><p>这个快捷栏可以使用鼠标右键调用出来</p><p>常用命令有以下几个</p><pre class="line-numbers language-none"><code class="language-none">ctrl + a:  全选ctrl + r:  测速(判断服务器是否超时)选中一个服务器后点击键盘上的 enter : 表示使用该服务器的代理<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922111436513.png" class="" title="image-20220922111436513"><h1 id="5-启动代理"><a href="#5-启动代理" class="headerlink" title="5.启动代理"></a>5.启动代理</h1><p>当我们选好一台代理服务器后，他应该长这样：图中蓝颜色的就是了，黑色的就是没有选中</p><p>那个<strong>测速结果只是判断能不能链接</strong>，<strong>不能连接的会提示你操作超时</strong>,能连接的会显示具体的延迟毫秒。</p><p><strong>理论上ms越大的速度越快</strong></p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922111716338.png" class="" title="image-20220922111716338"><p>选中服务器之后，回到屏幕的下方的菜单栏中找到v2rayN的软件,对其使用鼠标右键调用他的菜单栏</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922112012035.png" class="" title="image-20220922112012035"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922112059198.png" class="" title="image-20220922112059198"><p>选中自动配置系统代理后，图标会由蓝变红</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922112130848.png" class="" title="image-20220922112130848"><p>这时候就已经可以翻墙了</p><h3 id="效果如下"><a href="#效果如下" class="headerlink" title="效果如下"></a>效果如下</h3><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/22/zen-me-fan-qiang/image-20220922112210525.png" class="" title="image-20220922112210525">]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> 小技巧 </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>go建立第一个工程及变量配置</title>
      <link href="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/"/>
      <url>/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-环境变量问题"><a href="#1-环境变量问题" class="headerlink" title="1.环境变量问题"></a>1.环境变量问题</h1><p>在安装go编译器和goland的时候随手勾选添加到环境变量的选项即可</p><p>效果长这样</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921204933709.png" class="" title="image-20220921204933709"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921204823272.png" class="" title="image-20220921204823272"><p>Path中的</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921204854303.png" class="" title="image-20220921204854303"><h1 id="2-goland创建一个工程"><a href="#2-goland创建一个工程" class="headerlink" title="2.goland创建一个工程"></a>2.goland创建一个工程</h1><p><strong>file-setting</strong></p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205126572.png" class="" title="image-20220921205126572"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205144053.png" class="" title="image-20220921205144053"><p>在右上角 edit configuration或者 addconfiguration中配置下</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205343563.png" class="" title="image-20220921205343563"><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205314924.png" class="" title="image-20220921205314924"><p>正常new一个project然后在project目录下建立三个文件夹</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205103980.png" class="" title="image-20220921205103980"><h3 id="写一个代码"><a href="#写一个代码" class="headerlink" title="写一个代码"></a>写一个代码</h3><p>注意的是package需要些main而不是src</p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205403275.png" class="" title="image-20220921205403275"><p><strong>成功运行</strong></p><img src="/jcxj/2022/09/21/go-jian-li-di-yi-ge-gong-cheng-ji-bian-liang-pei-zhi/image-20220921205430038.png" class="" title="image-20220921205430038">]]></content>
      
      
      
